## Review Notes

- Source: `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/spinner/src/TxSpinner.vue` and `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/spinner/src/types.ts`.
- Screenshot: `.codex-screenshots/nexus-spinner-feedback-task-center-demo-playwright-2026-05-28.png`.
- Recommendation: Spinner does not communicate completion; switch to `TxProgressBar` for numeric progress and `TxLoadingState` when the panel needs a complete recovery path.
